              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27379163/" class="">第82页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/coincidence/" class=" " title="coincidence">coincidence</a>
                (年少轻狂。幸福时光。)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="27379163">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">在遇到她以前我不怕死，不惧远行，也不曾忧虑悠长岁月，现在却从未如此真切过地思虑起将来。</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27379163/">(<span class="">1回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-07-01 23:06</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">33人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>在遇到她以前我不怕死，不惧远行，也不曾忧虑悠长岁月，现在却从未如此真切过地思虑起将来。</q></blockquote>
